<lb n="1"/>śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1343 gunēṁṭi Āśvija śu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kla 15 mi śukravārānānu śrīmanmahāmaṁḍa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>lēsvaruṁḍaina Oḍḍādi pratāpārjjunadēparā(ṁ)ju
<lb n="4"/>tamakunu Ābīṣṭārtasidhigānu śrīnarasi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>hyanādhuniki nityamunnu sātukonu sama
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rpi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>cina Ābharaṇālu 15 <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> yu
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/><unclear>dōśasaṁsthisikila</unclear> 1 ki gadya <unclear>7</unclear> rū 8 mutyā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>la hāramu 1 ki mutyālu 182 ki gadya 13
<lb n="10"/>rū 3 paiṁḍipaṭikamu 1 ki nagarivīśenu vī 2 pa 7 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
